column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec, petroMag_u, petroMag_g, petroMag_r, petroMag_i, petroMag_z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, (#*s.z/#) as dist,  err_u, err_g, err_r, err_i, err_z, extinction_u, extinction_g, extinction_r, extinction_i, extinction_z, petroRad_g, petroRad_r FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = galaxy AND s.z># AND s.z<.#
